ADDITIONAL FINANCIAL DISCLAIMER

This software is provided as a technical demonstration of conversational AI
patterns for financial services. It is NOT:

  • A SEBI-registered investment advisory service
  • A licensed bank or NBFC
  • A payment processor or money-transfer service
  • A substitute for advice from a qualified financial professional

The included data (accounts, transactions, products, market prices, stocks,
indices) is entirely fictional. Names of banks, fintechs, brands, and
financial instruments are made up for demonstration purposes.

Do not deploy this software to handle real customer data, real money, or
make real financial decisions on behalf of end-users without substantial
modification, professional audit, and compliance with all applicable
regulations (RBI guidelines, SEBI regulations, IT Act, DPDP Act, etc.).

